Common Questions
----------------

### Is there a setup fee?

![Image 40](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5fc446238a88f40826c2ce10/5fc4462337773c58fefcbd50_icon-chevron-right.svg)

No. Account setup is included on all our plans. Our team is on hand to help you set up your account to get the most out of our platform. Reach out to us using the chat widget!

### We’re a non-profit organization. Is there special pricing available?

![Image 41](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5fc446238a88f40826c2ce10/5fc4462337773c58fefcbd50_icon-chevron-right.svg)

We’re proud to support NFP organizations. Get in touch to discuss special pricing for qualified not-for-profits.

Skedda is the complete workplace management software for managing desks, offices, visitors and other resources.
